This paper is about optimization algorithms for training deep learning models, which is a topic that falls under the machine learning (cs.LG) and neural networks (cs.NE) sub-categories. It also involves the use of various optimization techniques, which can be considered as artificial intelligence (cs.AI) methods. Additionally, the paper discusses the use of population-based optimization algorithms, which can be relevant to the data science (cs.DS) sub-category. Finally, the optimization algorithms can also be applied to control systems (cs.SY) in addition to machine learning.
